For a city slicker.

1016
00:55:19.356 --> 00:55:20.857
[ laughs ]

1017
00:55:25.995 --> 00:55:27.930
[ footsteps ]

1018
00:55:32.001 --> 00:55:33.370
Hi.
Hi.


1019
00:55:33.403 --> 00:55:35.372
Is Jared Barnes here?

1020
00:55:35.405 --> 00:55:37.173
Uh, yeah.

1021
00:55:37.206 --> 00:55:40.843
He's here,
but, uh, he's up
in my bathroom.


1022
00:55:40.877 --> 00:55:42.912
