1203
01:04:12.355 --> 01:04:14.624
This is very new to me.
[ laughs ]


1204
01:04:19.896 --> 01:04:20.897
[ laughs ]

1205
01:04:20.930 --> 01:04:22.865
Sit still.
Okay.


1206
01:04:22.899 --> 01:04:24.266
Open your eyes.

1207
01:04:24.301 --> 01:04:25.234
Oh, I'm sorry.

1208
01:04:26.836 --> 01:04:28.137
Good.

1209
01:04:41.351 --> 01:04:43.420
Am I allowed to talk?

1210
01:04:43.453 --> 01:04:44.821
Whatever you want.

1211
01:04:56.333 --> 01:04:57.634
Rae,

1212
01:04:57.667 --> 01:05:00.770
is that--Is that
short for Raymond?


1213
01:05:00.803 --> 01:05:02.572
[ laughs ]
No.


1214
01:05:02.605 --> 01:05:03.840
