1215
01:05:03.873 --> 01:05:06.609
but you can call me
Raymond if you like.


1216
01:05:06.643 --> 01:05:08.478
No, you know,
I might just--


1217
01:05:08.511 --> 01:05:09.779
Ahh. Ah, God.

1218
01:05:09.812 --> 01:05:11.681
What is it?
Are you okay?


1219
01:05:11.714 --> 01:05:13.716
Oh, it's my back.

1220
01:05:13.750 --> 01:05:16.786
It's got a life of its own,
likes to remind me.


1221
01:05:16.819 --> 01:05:18.955
Well, it shouldn't.
Let me help you.


1222
01:05:18.988 --> 01:05:20.423
Oh, boy.
Come here.


1223
01:05:20.457 --> 01:05:21.958
Okay. [ winces ]

1224
01:05:21.991 --> 01:05:22.959
You all right?

1225
01:05:22.992 --> 01:05:24.294
