1226
01:05:24.327 --> 01:05:26.363
Oh, man.

1227
01:05:26.396 --> 01:05:28.731
All right,
take off your shirt.


1228
01:05:28.765 --> 01:05:29.932
What?

1229
01:05:29.966 --> 01:05:30.933
Take off your shirt.

1230
01:05:30.967 --> 01:05:32.569
Lie down
