1239
01:05:47.717 --> 01:05:49.552
Ow.

1240
01:05:49.586 --> 01:05:53.390
There we go. Now...

1241
01:05:53.423 --> 01:05:54.524
[ gasping ]

1242
01:05:54.557 --> 01:05:56.626
