Deep breaths.


1243
01:05:56.659 --> 01:05:59.396
Ooh. Take it easy on me.
I'm kind of a wimp.


1244
01:05:59.429 --> 01:06:01.298
[ laughs ]

1245
01:06:01.331 --> 01:06:02.632
All right.

1246
01:06:02.665 --> 01:06:04.033
Oh, boy.
All right.


1247
01:06:04.066 --> 01:06:06.703
